{"type":"message","id":"5eddefeb","parentId":"d3fcea6b","timestamp":"2026-03-13T17:05:34.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what I can do. This is a general question about my capabilities. I should provide a helpful overview of what I can help with, keeping it concise but comprehensive.\n\nLet me think about the main categories:\n1. General assistance - answering questions, research, analysis\n2. File operations - reading, writing, editing files\n3. Web capabilities - search, fetch, browser automation\n4. Coding help - code review, debugging, spawning coding agents\n5. System operations - shell commands, process management\n6. Scheduling - cron jobs, reminders\n7. Messaging - sending messages across different platforms\n8. Browser control - screenshots, snapshots, automation\n9. Canvas/UI control\n10. Memory - I have memory files I can search and update\n11. PDF and image analysis\n12. Sub-agent spawning for complex tasks\n\nI should keep it friendly and aligned with my SOUL.md persona - genuinely helpful, not performative.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! I'm MoonViz, an AI assistant running inside OpenClaw. Here's what I can help you with:\n\n## Core Stuff\n- **Answer questions & research** — whether it's a quick fact or deep dive\n- **Read, write & edit files** — code, docs, notes, configs\n- **Run shell commands** — on your Mac or connected nodes\n- **Web search & browsing** — search the web, fetch pages, even control a browser for automation\n\n## Coding & Projects\n- **Code review & debugging** — look at your code, suggest fixes\n- **Spawn coding agents** — delegate bigger tasks to specialized agents (Codex, Claude Code, etc.)\n- **Analyze images & PDFs** — extract info, summarize, answer questions\n\n## System & Automation\n- **Schedule tasks & reminders** — set up cron jobs, one-time reminders\n- **Check memory** — I keep notes in MEMORY.md and daily logs so I remember context\n- **Manage processes** — background tasks, sub-agents\n\n## Communication\n- **Send messages** — if you've got channels set up (Discord, Telegram, etc.)\n\n## Quick Commands\n- `/status` — see what I'm up to\n- `/reasoning` — toggle detailed reasoning on/off\n\nWhat do you want to tackle?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":8124,"output":466,"cacheRead":4608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13198,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773421525879}}
